        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "A Symphony of Emotion: Beethoven Meets Einaudi - Chilliwack Cultural Centre"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Trio Fibonacci returns for another exciting concert, A Symphony of Emotion – Beethoven Meets Einaudi! Discover a new adaptation of the symphony for piano trio - a reminder of the days when large-scale works were performed in condensed form in the comfort of one’s own living room."
      }
    ],
